replies.bodyText:
Only if you want a connection. I actually need the URL with username/password to pass to the configuration. I wish it did have an easy way to do this.
If you don't care about the password, you could do something like this:
String jdbcUrl;
try (Connection connection = container.createConnection("")) {
    jdbcUrl = connection.getMetaData().getURL().toString();
}
But this seems overkill to just constructing it in one line.
